    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows visible signs of age, including some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor dents along the side panels. Inside, the upholstery has some wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully operational. Mechanically, it runs well, but it will likely need a new set of tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
