      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile engagement and precise shifts. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal power delivery. Finished in Titanium Silver, this example represents a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the canyons or the track.",
